gth last time out over 1400m at this track. Has a terrific record here with three wins and two placings from five starts. Best form puts her right in this. 6. BLACK VOLT turned in a fine effort to win by half a length at today's track and distance last start to maintain his good form of late. The engagement of Song Keong Yun is a positive move. Needs to be at his best to beat this field but he deserves plenty of thought. 2. VERLUC turned in a decent effort last start to finish third over 1600m at this track. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run.\",\"runners\":[5,1,6,2],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Korea Tips","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,5,2,6]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,7,2]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,2,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,8,6,7]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,7,10]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,10,5,11]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,2,6,5]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,2,6]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":4,"venueMnemonic":"BGM","raceType":"R"}},{"